  • Constructor Details

    • Sym_LZ4

      public Sym_LZ4​(int lenliterals, int matchlength, int offset, java.util.List<ISymbol> litterals)
      build a bit stream according to https://github.com/lz4/lz4/blob/master/doc/lz4_Block_format.md https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LZ4_(compression_algorithm) and also store the data of LZ4 algo. lenliterals=getS0().getId(); this is the number of the length of literals to follow matchlength==getS1().getId(); This is the length of the match copy operation offset=getS2().getId(); This is the possition of the match copy operation bit Stream : lenliterals[4]:matchlength[4](:offset[16])(:lenliterals[...])
